Reconcile EA App layout: rename, sweep, registry-aware symlinks

EA App fails in three related ways on Wine that the upstream
update_ea_path() does not handle:

1. Post-install detection race

2. Auto-update layout drift

3. Stale registry references

Four-step reconcile in update_ea_path (runs both from monitor_process
during install AND pre-launch via runner.py):


Adds "import re" (registry version scan) and "import shutil" (rmtree).
--- a/faugus/ea_fix.py
+++ b/faugus/ea_fix.py
@@ -1,5 +1,7 @@
